                        <h5 style="color: black; font-weight: bold;">Microscope</h5>
                        <p style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">High-resolution microscope for detailed observations.</p>
                        <a href="booking.html" class="btn btn-primary">Book Now</a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/images/equipment2.jpg" class="d-block" width="100%" height="600px" alt="Equipment 2">
