                        <h5 style="color: black; font-weight: bold;">3D Printer</h5>
                        <p style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Used for rapid prototyping and model making.</p>
                        <a href="booking.html" class="btn btn-primary">Book Now</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/images/equipment6.jpg" class="d-block" width="100%" height="600px" alt="Equipment 6">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block py-3" style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); border-radius: 10px; padding: 15px;">
                        <h5 style="color: black; font-weight: bold;">Tensile Testing Machine</h5>
                        <p style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">For testing material strength and elasticity.</p>
                        <a href="booking.html" class="btn btn-primary">Book Now</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/images/equipment7.jpg" class="d-block" width="100%" height="600px" alt="Equipment 7">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block py-3" style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); border-radius: 10px; padding: 15px;">
                        <h5 style="color: black; font-weight: bold;">Soldering Station</h5>
                        <p style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">Essential for assembling electronic circuits.</p>
                        <a href="booking.html" class="btn btn-primary">Book Now</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/images/equipment8.jpg" class="d-block" width="100%" height="600px" alt="Equipment 8">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block py-3" style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); border-radius: 10px; padding: 15px;">
                        <h5 style="color: black; font-weight: bold;">Function Generator</h5>
                        <p style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">For generating electrical waveforms.</p>
                        <a href="booking.html" class="btn btn-primary">Book Now</a>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/images/equipment9.jpg" class="d-block" width="100%" height="600px" alt="Equipment 9">
                    <div class="carousel-caption d-none d-md-block py-3" style="background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.5); border-radius: 10px; padding: 15px;">
                        <h5 style="color: black; font-weight: bold;">Hot Plate with Magnetic Stirrer</h5>
                        <p style="color: black; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;">For heating and stirring chemical solutions.</p>
